{"tid":814414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【古法按摩？】足浴女用口按摩啜腳 網民大呼噁心","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T08:41:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4000d8b142b6532b547c0ea7ff19d899aba9d7","tid":814414,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/09/11/8/81d92bb75dba51b6acdee094fc99cfb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F8%2F81d92bb75dba51b6acdee094fc99cfb1.jpg&h=a4f209d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵食艱難，這個說話香港人一定感受最深，大部分人出賣勞力、賣力工作，換來的微薄收入只能僅僅供大家「有尊嚴」地過生活，不過我們可能已經忘記了，其實很多時候我們都要放棄尊嚴地工作。日前網上流傳一段影片，一名足浴店女員工竟然用口為顧客進行腳底按摩，除了令網民大嘆噁心外，亦有人同情這位女工的遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n早前 Facebook 專頁「記錄中國 Record China 」分享一段影片，一名足浴店女員工先用白布包裹顧客的雙腳，然後竟直接用口輕咬對方雙腳，引來不少人旁觀，更有人舉機拍攝，拍下這個奇特的畫面，過程中這位女工似乎沒有一絲厭惡。<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jiluzg.3.0/videos/165546704310752/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjiluzg.3.0%2Fvideos%2F165546704310752%2F&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=356c50cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jiluzg.3.0/videos/165546704310752/</a><br />\n<br />\n不少網民看過影片後都大嘆噁心，除了涉及衛生問題外，更不明白用口按摩腳部有何作用，此外，也有網民同情這位女工的遭遇，認為她為了生活出賣自尊，令人不勝唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180911/1/67/1/%E5%8F%A4%E6%B3%95%E6%8C%89%E6%91%A9-%E8%B6%B3%E6%B5%B4%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8C%89%E6%91%A9%E5%95%9C%E8%85%B3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%91%BC%E5%99%81%E5%BF%83-9221037.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%2591%25A9-%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B4%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%2591%25A9%25E5%2595%259C%25E8%2585%25B3-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2591%25BC%25E5%2599%2581%25E5%25BF%2583-9221037.html&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3034016d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180911/1/67/1/%E5%8F%A4%E6%B3%95%E6%8C%89%E6%91%A9-%E8%B6%B3%E6%B5%B4%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8C%89%E6%91%A9%E5%95%9C%E8%85%B3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%91%BC%E5%99%81%E5%BF%83-9221037.html</a>"},{"pid":"ef53dbb63bb4932b7ff2c891d7987f262b0649c6","tid":814414,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:32:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"107c46e025efccff2306f0f0b5a81d130695b28c","tid":814414,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743f86031f8e1551267b4c2e5ec8f73a98c3c0c0","tid":814414,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"佢一定係腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350023c0f0453e0b1b4bf2a4fc73792cd7038bf7","tid":814414,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"叫佢幫我含佢都應該肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c530d03f152bf92a9e18f59c599113726daef61","tid":814414,"uid":205645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"個口實好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62e1916a8aa3ed2ed27bad8b64872529efb853c","tid":814414,"uid":810,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"可以加錢掉返轉？"},{"pid":"d82792b08f028fd378363b3985d55d5bea529738","tid":814414,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl